  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      450.65,
      272.04,
      533.71
    ],
    "text": "Very heavy showers above 150mm are likely at some places in Western, Sabaragamuwa and North-western provinces and in Kandy, Nuwara-Eliya, Galle and Matara districts.",
