      72.02,
      580.18,
      542.79,
      783.1
    ],
    "text": "Therefore, general public is advised to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by heavy rain, strong winds and lightning during thundershowers. Situation: Reported rainfall (currently received) from 08.30 a.m. on 14.05.2026 to 05.30 p.m. on 14.05.2026 given below.",
